  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 47b6fbf626d84142a85744b0f9e1e3dc, type: 3}
  m_Name: ExampleTRPGDialogueSequence
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  lines:
  - speakerName: Narrator
    text: 닫힌 철문 앞에 섰다. 어떻게 할까?
    enterActions: []
    choices:
    - text: 힘으로 밀어붙인다
      actions: []
      nextSequence: {fileID: 0}
      nextLineIndex: 2
      routes:
      - valueKey: forceDoorSuccess
        expectedValue: 1
        actions: []
        nextSequence: {fileID: 0}
        nextLineIndex: 1
    - text: 경비병을 설득한다
      actions: []
      nextSequence: {fileID: 0}
      nextLineIndex: 4
      routes:
      - valueKey: persuadeGuardSuccess
        expectedValue: 1
        actions: []
        nextSequence: {fileID: 0}
        nextLineIndex: 3
    - text: 경비병에게 10골드를 건넨다
      actions:
      - {fileID: 11400000, guid: 4e1b705b11594f81b9cde45709783eef, type: 2}
      nextSequence: {fileID: 0}
      nextLineIndex: 5
      routes: []
  - speakerName: Narrator
    text: 힘 판정 성공. 문이 크게 흔들리더니 천천히 열린다.
    enterActions: []
    choices:
    - text: 안으로 들어간다
      actions: []
      nextSequence: {fileID: 0}
      nextLineIndex: 6
      routes: []
  - speakerName: Narrator
    text: 힘 판정 실패. 문은 꿈쩍도 하지 않고 어깨만 얼얼하다.
    enterActions: []
    choices:
    - text: 물러난다
      actions: []
      nextSequence: {fileID: 0}
      nextLineIndex: -1
      routes: []
  - speakerName: Guard
    text: 설득 성공. 경비병이 한숨을 쉬며 문을 열어준다.
    enterActions: []
    choices:
    - text: 고맙다고 말한다
      actions: []
      nextSequence: {fileID: 0}
      nextLineIndex: 6
      routes: []
  - speakerName: Guard
    text: 설득 실패. 경비병은 팔짱을 낀 채 고개를 젓는다.
    enterActions: []
    choices:
    - text: 10골드를 내민다
      actions:
      - {fileID: 11400000, guid: 4e1b705b11594f81b9cde45709783eef, type: 2}
      nextSequence: {fileID: 0}
      nextLineIndex: 5
      routes: []
    - text: 돌아간다
      actions: []
      nextSequence: {fileID: 0}
      nextLineIndex: -1
      routes: []
  - speakerName: Guard
    text: 경비병이 금화를 받아 챙기고 문을 열어준다. 골드가 10 감소했다.
    enterActions: []
    choices:
    - text: 안으로 들어간다
      actions: []
      nextSequence: {fileID: 0}
      nextLineIndex: 6
      routes: []
  - speakerName: Narrator
    text: 당신은 문 너머 어두운 복도로 들어선다.
    enterActions: []
    choices:
    - text: 대화를 끝낸다
      actions: []
      nextSequence: {fileID: 0}
      nextLineIndex: -1
      routes: []
